  "3027810": {
    "name": "东方诡夜行",
    "steam_appid": 3027810,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/65583d35307b465e9ae450c5bdab2813.avif?t=1726726595\" width=562 height=280 /></span><br>《东方诡夜行》是一款Roguelike角色扮演类的东方Project同人游戏。在这个游戏中，你将会扮演一支团队在幻想乡这个东方世界观的主舞台里四处奔波，接受朋友们的帮助、与敌人战斗、以及遭遇各种随机的事件，并最终决定幻想乡今后的命运。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/5d1cfaa208c29d4a244edcd735f853b2.avif?t=1726726595\" width=562 height=392 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆幻想乡最后的夜晚</h2>来自地狱的埴轮军团入侵了幻想乡，它们得到了未知的力量，甚至足以将幻想乡毁灭。<br><i><strong>今夜已然被刻进了无尽的噩梦之中…但或许你可以拯救这一切！</strong></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/0aa06863fff02f6d6e8ad45316f32e8f.poster.avif?t=1726726595\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/0aa06863fff02f6d6e8ad45316f32e8f.webm?t=1726726595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/0aa06863fff02f6d6e8ad45316f32e8f.mp4?t=1726726595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆英雄集结！</h2>选择三位你喜欢的东方角色，踏上这场注定不平凡的征程。<br><i><strong>尝试不同的组合，构建出一套属于你的强大的阵容！</strong></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/54dbdac31a98dcb1fa4be5d44e1ce946.poster.avif?t=1726726595\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/54dbdac31a98dcb1fa4be5d44e1ce946.webm?t=1726726595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/54dbdac31a98dcb1fa4be5d44e1ce946.mp4?t=1726726595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆特别的即时回合制战斗</h2>敌人和角色都会随着时间的流逝获得行动点，角色甚至能保留这些行动点以稍后使用。在战斗中你可以随时停止时间以观察局势，敌人的所有行动也都将由你来决定。<br><i><strong>等待机会还是立即攻击？亦或者先在敌人的行动中做出抉择？</strong></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/64bc8ce280da83f170d1f04593370518.poster.avif?t=1726726595\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/64bc8ce280da83f170d1f04593370518.webm?t=1726726595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/64bc8ce280da83f170d1f04593370518.mp4?t=1726726595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆遵从市场神的指引</h2>在市场神的影响下，如今的幻想乡可得靠钱办事了。强力好用的道具都明码标价，只要你有钱就能快速提升战斗力。你可以出售掉用不上的道具、去赌场玩骰子、或者是尝试解开保险箱的密码、甚至你可以通过宗教的影响力来赚信徒们的钱…<br><i><strong>别担心，他们都是自愿的。</strong></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/d24330e5b1528316ef36017fb63e70d9.poster.avif?t=1726726595\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/d24330e5b1528316ef36017fb63e70d9.webm?t=1726726595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/d24330e5b1528316ef36017fb63e70d9.mp4?t=1726726595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆多种多样的玩法</h2>在冒险中当然也需要适当的娱乐，除了多样的地点和事件外，《东方诡夜行》中还包含很多小型游戏：骰子赌博、数字解谜、卡牌构筑、身份推理…<br><i><strong>这些小型游戏不会对游戏流程造成太大的影响，你主要是为了从中获得一些额外的奖励。</strong></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/0d83169389b09165ca5ab69d5e6e9931.poster.avif?t=1726726595\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/0d83169389b09165ca5ab69d5e6e9931.webm?t=1726726595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/0d83169389b09165ca5ab69d5e6e9931.mp4?t=1726726595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆角色养成和情绪管理</h2>在提升角色们的战斗能力的同时，也要注意到她们的情绪变化：角色会因为连续的战斗感到疲惫不堪、因为信仰的分歧而心存芥蒂、因为朋友的死亡而自责懊悔…一旦角色情绪崩溃，她将会做出不理智的行为。<br><i><strong>在痛苦面前，没有人能当得了英雄…</strong></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/86ea16abdd10f10c787b193e6087b6fd.poster.avif?t=1726726595\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/86ea16abdd10f10c787b193e6087b6fd.webm?t=1726726595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027810/extras/86ea16abdd10f10c787b193e6087b6fd.mp4?t=1726726595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆交流讨论</h2><br>交流讨论QQ群：1006543991",
